extends baseEmail

block content
  h2 Dispatch Notification
  p Hello,
  p We hope this email finds you well. We want to inform you that your package sent from #{userName} currently on transit to your. Here are the details:

  table(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;")
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Package Name:
      td #{packageName}
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Tracking Number:
      td [#{trackingNumber}]
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Tracking Password (To be used together with the tracking number for tracking package location.):
      td [#{trackingPassword}]
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Sender's Phone Number:
      td [#{phoneNumber}] 
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Destination:
      td [#{destination}]
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Status:
      td #{status}
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Estimated Time of Arrival:
      td #{ETA}
    tr
      td(style="font-weight: bold; width:200px") Dispatch Date:
      td #{dispatchDate}

  p For for tracking, kindly request a password from the center.
  p Please note that the package is currently in transit and may take some time to reach its destination. We appreciate your patience.
  p Thank you for choosing our services. We look forward to delivering your package successfully.
  p Best regards,
  p Real Logistics Inc

  p For questions and enquiries you can reach us via-
  p email: gozieelendu@gmail.com
